{% set zone = states('sensor.demerit_zone') | trim %}
{% if zone == 'red' %}<center><b><font color="#e53935">RED ZONE</font></b></center>
{% elif zone == 'orange' %}<center><b><font color="#fb8c00">ORANGE ZONE</font></b></center>
{% elif zone == 'yellow' %}<center><b><font color="#fdd835">YELLOW ZONE</font></b></center>
{% elif zone == 'green' %}<center><b><font color="#43a047">GREEN ZONE</font></b></center>
{% endif %}

{% set zone = states('sensor.demerit_zone') | trim %}
{% set pts = states('input_number.demerit_points') | int(0) %}
{% set exempt = is_state('input_boolean.exemption_today', 'on') %}

{% if exempt %}
🛋️ **Exemption day — all blocks lifted.** Everything accessible. Rules return at midnight.
{% elif zone == 'green' %}
✅ **Nothing blocked.** You're at **{{ pts }}/12** — full access.
{% elif zone == 'yellow' %}
🟡 **Yellow zone — blocked:** YouTube, Instagram

🟢 **Still allowed:** Netflix, Prime, JioHotstar, Brave

You're at **{{ pts }}/12**. Reach **9** for full access ({{ 9 - pts }} more pts).
{% elif zone == 'orange' %}
🟠 **Orange zone — blocked:** YouTube, Instagram, Netflix, Prime

🟢 **Still allowed:** JioHotstar, Brave, WhatsApp, work apps

You're at **{{ pts }}/12**. Reach **6** for yellow ({{ 6 - pts }} pts), **9** for green.
{% elif zone == 'red' %}
🔴 **Red zone — blocked:** YouTube, Instagram, Netflix, Prime, JioHotstar

🟢 **Still allowed:** Brave, WhatsApp, work apps

You're at **{{ pts }}/12**. Reach **3** for orange ({{ 3 - pts }} pts), **6** for yellow.
{% endif %}

_WhatsApp CDN, Brave, work apps always allowed._
